data.text: @RoyallyPetite The Schleswig Holstein Sonderburg Glücksburgs were still a little peeved that he had dropped the family name, and adopted the anglicised version of his mother's maiden name (Battenberg), so that he could court his 13-year old cousin.

@RoyallyPetite Hardly the same thing.  The press did not go in a tizzy about the lack of invites for 3 sisters.  Marina flew to germany a few days later to bring them the news about it. 3 years Margarita was one of Anne’s godmothers. Markle 1/2 sibs will never invited
